<div class="page">
  <header class="section-header">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">StackScope</p>
      <h1>New server</h1>
      <p>Add a new node and point it to the agent.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="toolbar">
      <%= link_to "Back", servers_path, class: "button ghost" %>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="form-card">
    <%= render "form", server: @server %>
  </div>

  <div class="note">
    <h3>How to install the agent</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Build the binary: <code>cd agent &amp;&amp; go build -o stackscope-agent</code></li>
      <li>Run on the server: <code>STACKSCOPE_TOKEN="secret" ./stackscope-agent -addr ":9100"</code></li>
      <li>Set Agent URL to: <code>http://&lt;ip&gt;:9100/metrics</code></li>
      <li>If you use a token, set it in the Agent token field.</li>
    </ol>
    <p>Status checks use TCP to the port (if set), otherwise port 80.</p>
  </div>
</div>
